Name: Run Selection with Status
Description: Run selected R code through the RStudio Console and show Running, Complete, Fail, or Interrupted in the macOS menu bar.
Binding: run_selection_with_status
Interactive: false

Name: Run Current Document with Status
Description: Run the current R document through the RStudio Console and show its status in the macOS menu bar.
Binding: run_current_document_with_status
Interactive: false
